data.description: Back on Market no fault of the sellers, buyers got cold feet! Come check out this beautiful 3 bedroom with 2-1/2 bathrooms country home on 4 acres just outside of the city. Nice open floor plan with the master suite and laundry on the main floor, with 2 more bedrooms downstairs and a huge rec room. With an attached 2 car garage and a generous sized storage room in the basement space is not an issue here. The master suite is on the main floor with a nice size master bathroom, laundry, and a generous walk-in closet. True hardwood floors throughout the main floor and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the lower level. This home sits on 4 acres and is right down the road from 172 acres of conservation land perfect for hunting. If you have been looking for a little bit of space without getting too far from the city you have found it. The pasture is cross fenced so its ready for a couple horses or whatever your heart desires. This home will qualify for FHA, VA, and USDA loans!
